691
00:28:47,050 --> 00:28:49,372
un fun dem hot men ⟨getrogn⟩ vaser.

692
00:28:49,429 --> 00:28:53,451
es iz geven mener vos zey hobn gehat veser, hobn arayngegosn, un zey hobn

693
00:28:53,451 --> 00:28:55,363
gefirt tsu di mentshn.

694
00:28:55,133 --> 00:28:56,544
a vaser treger.

695
00:28:56,162 --> 00:28:58,636
a vaser tre- UNK veys, a vaser treger.

696
00:28:58,288 --> 00:29:00,189
un s'iz geven elektrye?

697
00:29:00,634 --> 00:29:02,400
elektrye shoyn gevezn.

698
00:29:02,575 --> 00:29:04,442
BEGINNING hot gehat lemp

699
00:29:04,515 --> 00:29:06,368
mit GAS. nakher

700
00:29:06,368 --> 00:29:08,166
nisht yeder hot gehat elektrye.

701
00:29:08,166 --> 00:29:10,028
a sakh hobn nokh nisht gehat keyn elektrye.

702
00:29:09,830 --> 00:29:10,910
ir hot gehat?

703
00:29:10,253 --> 00:29:12,761
oh, undz ho- m'hot ⟨dokh⟩ gedorfn naye

704
00:29:13,341 --> 00:29:17,250
⟨nokh⟩ gedorfn zen. yedes mol hot UNK dos gloz geplatst

705
00:29:17,425 --> 00:29:20,712
un azoy vi s'iz gevorn elektrye hot men di ershte gemakht elektrye.

